prompt_template:
You are an expert patent classifier. Your task is to classify the following patent into exactly one of these categories: {categories}

Patent text:
{text}

Analyze the patent content and respond with a JSON object in this exact format:
{{
    "predicted_label": "<the most appropriate category from the list>",
    "confidence": <a number between 0 and 1 indicating your confidence>,
    "scores": {{
        "<category1>": <score between 0 and 1>,
        "<category2>": <score between 0 and 1>
    }}
}}

Important:
- The predicted_label MUST be exactly one of the categories provided
- All scores should sum to approximately 1.0
- Respond ONLY with the JSON object, no additional text
